\ An unterminated quotation inside a definition (a [: / [> / [| with no
\ matching :]) must fail loudly and discard the half-built word, not segfault.
\ The system must recover and keep compiling/running normally afterward.

: bad [: 1 2 ;
bad
: bad2 [> a b | a ;
bad2
1 2 + .
: good 6 7 + ;
good .
[ 1 2 3 ] [: dup * :] map .
cr
